", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganisofficially came out at the Gay Games in 1994, and went public with his HIV status in 1995, with the release of his memoir \\\"Breaking the Surface.\\\"\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Gay Games\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"his HIV status\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the release\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"his memoir\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the Surface\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's interesting,\\\" he says now, \\\"all these years later, I was prepared to die.\\\"\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He pauses for a beat and adds, \\\"I wasn't prepared to live.\\\"\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beat\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Louganis poses with his two gold medals during the Summer Olympics XXIII in 1984 in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999995688745932, \"rank\": 1.555307597856036e-07, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his two gold medals\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics XXIII\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Focus on Sport via Getty Images) To appreciate the magnitude of Louganis' transformative impact, you need only look as far asthose Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._Paul_Getty_Museum\", \"score\": 0.6236381162350415, \"rank\": 0.3885368592133646, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._Paul_Getty_Museum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._Paul_Getty_Museum\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the magnitude\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' transformative impact\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris Games\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese team's masterful domination of the diving competitions (six golds and counting), rooted in its unstoppable combination of precision and grace, has clear precedent in Louganis' groundbreaking, gymnastic style.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9925236642448093, \"rank\": 0.004737041490741494, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the diving competitions\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"six golds\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"counting\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"its unstoppable combination\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"precision\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"grace\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"clear precedent\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' groundbreaking, gymnastic style\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They used me as a model in their diving program,\\\" says Louganis, who trained as an acrobat and dancer as a child before moving to diving.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a model\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"their diving program\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"an acrobat\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"dancer\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They pull the kids out when they are very, very young, and introduce them to dance and acrobatics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That type of balance and rhythm exposure,\\\" he notes, \\\"are the skill sets that you are going to use and need to become a good diver.\\\"\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That type\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"balance and rhythm exposure\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"the skill sets\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"a good diver\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis' influence extends far beyond the perimeter of the pool.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis' influence\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"the perimeter\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Paris Games this year, there arenearly 200 LGBTQ+ athletes.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"200 LGBTQ+ athletes\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three decades ago, Louganis was among just a small handful of openly gay elite athletes in the world.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"just a small handful\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"openly gay elite athletes\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was also one of the first to disclose he was HIV-positive.As the New York Times grimly reported in 1995, \\\"Louganis now has the dreadful distinction of being the world's most prominent athlete to say he contacted AIDS from homosexual activity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999995332963133, \"rank\": 3.990770675645794e-07, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"the dreadful distinction\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most prominent athlete\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"AIDS\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"homosexual activity\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now,exactly 40 years after he earned his first gold, his distinctions would never be referred to as \\\"dreadful.\\\"\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 3036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first gold\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"his distinctions\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he's back at the Olympics, as an ambassador forPride House Paris, a space for athletes and fans from the LGBTQ+ community and their allies to celebrate this year's games and socialize.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.8098089021774426, \"rank\": 0.2333307026554293, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\"}, {\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9991696526224746, \"rank\": 0.0008310374273080494, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"a space\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3127}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"the LGBTQ+ community\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"their allies\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's games\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did this shy, adopted child, a kid bullied at school for his dark skin, his stutter, his dyslexia and his interest in - and uncanny aptitude for - \\\"sissy\\\" pursuits like gymnastics become one of the most visible and outspoken LGBTQ+ athletes in the world?\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"his dark skin\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"his stutter\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"his dyslexia\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"his interest\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"uncanny aptitude\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3371}, {\"ngram\": \"- \\\"sissy\\\" pursuits\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"the most visible and outspoken LGBTQ+ athletes\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related Louganis first learned to dive in his family swimming pool.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Related Louganis\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"his family swimming pool\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When knee problems ruled out his other athletic activities, diving became his primary focus.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"knee problems\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"his other athletic activities\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"his primary focus\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the age of 16, just as he was coming to terms with his sexuality, he was competing in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"his sexuality\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There he earned his first medal, a silver, for the 10-meter platform.\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first medal\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3793}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-meter platform\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The achievement made him instantly renowned.\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The achievement\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he says that silver only made him feel like \\\"the first loser.\\\"\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"the first loser\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are riddled with guilt, as gay individuals, because we are told we are wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 4017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guilt\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"gay individuals\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He remembers the scene in Montreal in 1976.\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4045, \"end\": 4053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"score\": 0.9976146367857964, \"rank\": 0.0023498389911947885, \"text\": \"Montreal\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the time, I was training with [former Olympic champion]Dr. Sammy Lee.\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4132, \"end\": 4135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9436850638316888, \"rank\": 0.057029645287664854, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"former Olympic champion]Dr\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Klaus Dibiase from Italy was going for his third Olympic gold medal,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4156, \"end\": 4161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7949046916230035, \"rank\": 0.24041962810959006, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Klaus Dibiase\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"his third Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The training I was doing was all about beating Klaus, so my sole purpose on this planet was to prevent Klaus from winning that gold medal.\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The training\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4229}, {\"ngram\": \"Klaus\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4269}, {\"ngram\": \"my sole purpose\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4289}, {\"ngram\": \"this planet\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"Klaus\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4325}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold medal\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I failed, and Dr. Lee let me know that I failed.\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4374, \"end\": 4377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9436850638316888, \"rank\": 0.057029645287664854, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was pretty brutal.\\\"\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already prone to depression and suicidal ideation, Louganis' post-Olympic victory lap was anything but.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 4448, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"suicidal ideation\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4480}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' post-Olympic victory lap\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not understand when I went back to high school why everybody was celebrating me when I felt like such a failure,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4588}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"such a failure\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was almost a statistic.\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statistic\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried to commit suicide.\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"suicide\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought the world would be a better place without me.\\\"\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4738}, {\"ngram\": \"a better place\", \"from\": 4748, \"to\": 4762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were also rumors about his sexuality, rumblings that occasionally manifested in slurs and offensive signs at his tournaments.\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rumors\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4799}, {\"ngram\": \"his sexuality\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4819}, {\"ngram\": \"rumblings\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"slurs\", \"from\": 4863, \"to\": 4868}, {\"ngram\": \"offensive signs\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4888}, {\"ngram\": \"his tournaments\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 4907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tactics did not get under his skin, though.\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tactics\", \"from\": 4909, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"his skin\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's easy to point to homophobia, the'f*g buster' campaign,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"homophobia\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 4990}, {\"ngram\": \"the'f*g buster' campaign\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But years later, and meeting up with a lot of these guys, it was more about jealousy.\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5071}, {\"ngram\": \"these guys\", \"from\": 5075, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"jealousy\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was winning, and I get it - if you can not beat him on the boards, then you beat him off the boards.\", \"from\": 5115, \"to\": 5217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boards\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5182}, {\"ngram\": \"the boards\", \"from\": 5206, \"to\": 5216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not know that all of it was homophobia.\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that a lot of it was just jealousy.\\\"\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Louganis of the United States competes in the diving competition off the Springboard during the 1984 Summer Olympics in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5312, \"end\": 5325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}, {\"begin\": 5333, \"end\": 5346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7423054847273731, \"rank\": 0.34367301860102434, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5437, \"end\": 5448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999917637912112, \"rank\": 5.683031538316831e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the diving competition\", \"from\": 5359, \"to\": 5381}, {\"ngram\": \"the Springboard\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5401}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1984 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 5409, \"to\": 5433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Focus on Sport/Getty Images) After sitting out the 1980 Moscow Olympics because ofthe U.S. boycott, the El Cajon native returned to earn two golds on his home turf at the 1984 Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5538, \"end\": 5550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics_boycott\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"U.S. boycott\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics_boycott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics_boycott\"}, {\"begin\": 5556, \"end\": 5564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Cajon_Boulevard\", \"score\": 0.9949560129390455, \"rank\": 0.005068501294013292, \"text\": \"El Cajon\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Cajon_Boulevard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/El_Cajon_Boulevard\"}, {\"begin\": 5637, \"end\": 5648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999917637912112, \"rank\": 5.683031538316831e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Focus\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5456}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport/Getty Images\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5478}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1980 Moscow Olympics\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 5588, \"to\": 5597}, {\"ngram\": \"his home turf\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5614}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1984 Games\", \"from\": 5618, \"to\": 5632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was meant to be his farewell.\", \"from\": 5650, \"to\": 5682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his farewell\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it turned into one of his first acts of advocacy.\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first acts\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"advocacy\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was supposed to retire after 1984,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got my two Olympic gold medals,broke 700 on the 10-meter platform.I went to the nationals and I brokeCynthia Potter'srecord for national championship titles.\", \"from\": 5791, \"to\": 5951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my two Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5824}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-meter platform\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 5859}, {\"ngram\": \"the nationals\", \"from\": 5870, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"national championship titles\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was fully prepared to move on.\\\"\", \"from\": 5952, \"to\": 5985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was going to pack up my bags, go back to California, lock myself in my house and wait to die.\\\"\", \"from\": 5987, \"to\": 6084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6031, \"end\": 6041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\", \"score\": 0.9103285519411718, \"rank\": 0.0984996755128408, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my bags\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6018}, {\"ngram\": \"my house\", \"from\": 6058, \"to\": 6066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not quite work out that way.\", \"from\": 6086, \"to\": 6121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight years into his Olympic career, Louganis was - like many successful Olympians -a sought-after public figure.\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic career\", \"from\": 6140, \"to\": 6158}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 6160, \"to\": 6168}, {\"ngram\": \"many successful Olympians\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6205}, {\"ngram\": \"sought-after public figure\", \"from\": 6209, \"to\": 6235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But because of InternationalOlympic Committee rules at the time, there were strict guidelines around what they could do and how they could be paid, often leaving athletes financially strapped -an issue that persists 40 years later.\", \"from\": 6237, \"to\": 6468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"InternationalOlympic Committee rules\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6288}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6300}, {\"ngram\": \"strict guidelines\", \"from\": 6313, \"to\": 6330}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6399, \"to\": 6407}, {\"ngram\": \"-an issue\", \"from\": 6429, \"to\": 6438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Edwin Moses[the Olympic gold medalist hurdler] and I were pushing for trust funds for athletes that they can draw on, so they can do commercials, speaking and appearances.\", \"from\": 6470, \"to\": 6642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trust funds\", \"from\": 6541, \"to\": 6552}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 6557, \"to\": 6565}, {\"ngram\": \"commercials\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That goes into their trust fund, and they can utilize that money for their training and living expenses beyond college.\", \"from\": 6643, \"to\": 6762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their trust fund\", \"from\": 6658, \"to\": 6674}, {\"ngram\": \"that money\", \"from\": 6697, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"their training and living expenses\", \"from\": 6712, \"to\": 6746}, {\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 6754, \"to\": 6761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was a part of that.\", \"from\": 6763, \"to\": 6784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 6769, \"to\": 6775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was an athlete rep.\\\" (Notably, neither Moses nor Louganis received the typical Olympic champion honor ofa Wheaties box placementuntil 2015.)\", \"from\": 6785, \"to\": 6927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6893, \"end\": 6901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wheaties\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete rep\", \"from\": 6791, \"to\": 6805}, {\"ngram\": \"neither Moses\", \"from\": 6818, \"to\": 6831}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 6836, \"to\": 6844}, {\"ngram\": \"the typical Olympic champion honor\", \"from\": 6854, \"to\": 6888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the nationals, I went to [USA diving president] Phil Boggs and said, 'What's going on with trust funds?'\", \"from\": 6929, \"to\": 7040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6984, \"end\": 6994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Boggs\", \"score\": 0.9999949567770569, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phil Boggs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Boggs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Boggs\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nationals\", \"from\": 6936, \"to\": 6949}, {\"ngram\": \"USA diving president\", \"from\": 6962, \"to\": 6982}, {\"ngram\": \"trust funds\", \"from\": 7027, \"to\": 7038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, 'Well, the only one that it affects is you and you are retiring.\", \"from\": 7041, \"to\": 7114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we do not have to spend the money on attorneys to get the trust funds to put it in place.'\", \"from\": 7115, \"to\": 7208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 7142, \"to\": 7151}, {\"ngram\": \"attorneys\", \"from\": 7155, \"to\": 7164}, {\"ngram\": \"the trust funds\", \"from\": 7172, \"to\": 7187}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 7201, \"to\": 7206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said, 'Fine, I am not retiring.\", \"from\": 7209, \"to\": 7242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do your f**king homework.'\\\"\", \"from\": 7243, \"to\": 7270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your f**king homework\", \"from\": 7246, \"to\": 7267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(The International Swimming Hall of Fame, meanwhile remembers Boggs as the person who\\\"helped create the Athletes Trust fund.\\\")\", \"from\": 7271, \"to\": 7397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7333, \"end\": 7338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hale_Boggs\", \"score\": 0.9946493689635718, \"rank\": 0.005379380809691167, \"text\": \"Boggs\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hale_Boggs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hale_Boggs\"}, {\"begin\": 7384, \"end\": 7394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_law\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trust fund\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_law\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trust_law\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fame\", \"from\": 7307, \"to\": 7311}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 7342, \"to\": 7352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was really angry,\\\" Louganis remembers.\", \"from\": 7399, \"to\": 7440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My intent was to stay eligible until the trust funds were put into place, because I felt that was going to be my legacy.\", \"from\": 7441, \"to\": 7562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My intent\", \"from\": 7442, \"to\": 7451}, {\"ngram\": \"the trust funds\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7494}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 7509, \"to\": 7514}, {\"ngram\": \"my legacy\", \"from\": 7552, \"to\": 7561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took two years.\", \"from\": 7563, \"to\": 7581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 7571, \"to\": 7580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In those two years, I found myself at the World Championships, and I won.\", \"from\": 7582, \"to\": 7655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those two years\", \"from\": 7585, \"to\": 7600}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 7620, \"to\": 7643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My coach, Ron O'Brien, said, 'What are you going to do?\", \"from\": 7656, \"to\": 7711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7666, \"end\": 7677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_O'Brien_(coach)\", \"score\": 0.9999952755200829, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ron O'Brien\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_O'Brien_(coach)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_O'Brien_(coach)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My coach\", \"from\": 7656, \"to\": 7664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just two more years.'\", \"from\": 7712, \"to\": 7738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just two more years\", \"from\": 7717, \"to\": 7736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how Seoul happened.\", \"from\": 7739, \"to\": 7765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7750, \"end\": 7755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9977970472302476, \"rank\": 0.002195961652529736, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't supposed to happen for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 7766, \"to\": 7803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Louganis during the 1987 U.S. National Diving Championships (Getty Images/Tony Duffy/ALLSPORT) By 1988,AIDS had become a full-blown public health crisis.\", \"from\": 7805, \"to\": 7964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7805, \"end\": 7818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1987 U.S. National Diving Championships\", \"from\": 7826, \"to\": 7869}, {\"ngram\": \"Getty Images/Tony Duffy\", \"from\": 7871, \"to\": 7894}, {\"ngram\": \"ALLSPORT\", \"from\": 7895, \"to\": 7903}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-blown public health crisis\", \"from\": 7929, \"to\": 7962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis had been training in Florida when he got the diagnosis, six months before the Seoul Games.\", \"from\": 7965, \"to\": 8064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7995, \"end\": 8002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.999968987989733, \"rank\": 2.062633731287561e-05, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 7965, \"to\": 7973}, {\"ngram\": \"the diagnosis\", \"from\": 8015, \"to\": 8028}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seoul Games\", \"from\": 8048, \"to\": 8063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was having something going on with my ear,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 8065, \"to\": 8120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8079, \"to\": 8088}, {\"ngram\": \"my ear\", \"from\": 8103, \"to\": 8109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went to the doctor, my cousin who was treating me.\", \"from\": 8121, \"to\": 8174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the doctor\", \"from\": 8132, \"to\": 8142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I did the test, my thought was, if I am positive, I was going to pack up my bags, go back to California, lock myself in my house and wait to die.\\\"\", \"from\": 8175, \"to\": 8326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8273, \"end\": 8283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999912661085646, \"rank\": 7.336014401068997e-06, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 8186, \"to\": 8194}, {\"ngram\": \"my thought\", \"from\": 8196, \"to\": 8206}, {\"ngram\": \"my bags\", \"from\": 8253, \"to\": 8260}, {\"ngram\": \"my house\", \"from\": 8300, \"to\": 8308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because that's what we thought of HIV,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 8328, \"to\": 8377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HIV\", \"from\": 8363, \"to\": 8366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's difficult to express the profound terror and grief of the first several years of the AIDS crisis to those who did not endure them.\", \"from\": 8379, \"to\": 8514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the profound terror\", \"from\": 8405, \"to\": 8424}, {\"ngram\": \"grief\", \"from\": 8429, \"to\": 8434}, {\"ngram\": \"the first several years\", \"from\": 8438, \"to\": 8461}, {\"ngram\": \"the AIDS crisis\", \"from\": 8465, \"to\": 8480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Death felt omnipresent.\", \"from\": 8515, \"to\": 8538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Death\", \"from\": 8515, \"to\": 8520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In cities like New York and San Francisco, cadaverous young men with lesions on their arms and faces were a frequent sight.\", \"from\": 8539, \"to\": 8662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8554, \"end\": 8562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9998543618010851, \"rank\": 0.00014139607775438085, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 8567, \"end\": 8580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\", \"score\": 0.9999926062326304, \"rank\": 7.058138739068921e-06, \"text\": \"San Francisco\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Francisco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 8542, \"to\": 8548}, {\"ngram\": \"cadaverous young men\", \"from\": 8582, \"to\": 8602}, {\"ngram\": \"lesions\", \"from\": 8608, \"to\": 8615}, {\"ngram\": \"their arms\", \"from\": 8619, \"to\": 8629}, {\"ngram\": \"faces\", \"from\": 8634, \"to\": 8639}, {\"ngram\": \"a frequent sight\", \"from\": 8645, \"to\": 8661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex with a new partner was often a fraught negotiation.\", \"from\": 8663, \"to\": 8718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sex\", \"from\": 8663, \"to\": 8666}, {\"ngram\": \"a new partner\", \"from\": 8672, \"to\": 8685}, {\"ngram\": \"a fraught negotiation\", \"from\": 8696, \"to\": 8717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when there were so few treatment options and so much still unknown, when a ravaging virus was in some circles regarded as a convenient excuse for homophobia, disclosure of one's HIV status could have devastating personal and professional consequences.\", \"from\": 8719, \"to\": 8974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so few treatment options\", \"from\": 8739, \"to\": 8763}, {\"ngram\": \"a ravaging virus\", \"from\": 8796, \"to\": 8812}, {\"ngram\": \"some circles\", \"from\": 8820, \"to\": 8832}, {\"ngram\": \"a convenient excuse\", \"from\": 8845, \"to\": 8864}, {\"ngram\": \"homophobia\", \"from\": 8869, \"to\": 8879}, {\"ngram\": \"disclosure\", \"from\": 8881, \"to\": 8891}, {\"ngram\": \"one's HIV status\", \"from\": 8895, \"to\": 8911}, {\"ngram\": \"devastating personal and professional consequences\", \"from\": 8923, \"to\": 8973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They did say, 'Tone the gay thing down.'\\\"\", \"from\": 8976, \"to\": 9018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gay thing\", \"from\": 8997, \"to\": 9010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 1988,\\\" he remembers, \\\"our friends in the gay community were dying.\", \"from\": 9020, \"to\": 9090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our friends\", \"from\": 9046, \"to\": 9057}, {\"ngram\": \"the gay community\", \"from\": 9061, \"to\": 9078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had as many as six, seven, and eight memorials to go to on a weekend.\", \"from\": 9091, \"to\": 9163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight memorials\", \"from\": 9125, \"to\": 9140}, {\"ngram\": \"a weekend\", \"from\": 9153, \"to\": 9162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was crazy.\", \"from\": 9164, \"to\": 9177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, there were people saying, 'It's killing the right people.\", \"from\": 9178, \"to\": 9245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9199, \"to\": 9205}, {\"ngram\": \"the right people\", \"from\": 9228, \"to\": 9244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's killing gay men and IV drug users and prostitutes.'\", \"from\": 9246, \"to\": 9302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gay men\", \"from\": 9259, \"to\": 9266}, {\"ngram\": \"IV drug users\", \"from\": 9271, \"to\": 9284}, {\"ngram\": \"prostitutes\", \"from\": 9289, \"to\": 9300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a real judgment surrounding it, and also guilt.\", \"from\": 9303, \"to\": 9360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real judgment\", \"from\": 9313, \"to\": 9328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are riddled with guilt, as gay individuals, because we are told we are wrong.\", \"from\": 9361, \"to\": 9441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guilt\", \"from\": 9381, \"to\": 9386}, {\"ngram\": \"gay individuals\", \"from\": 9391, \"to\": 9406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We get that message, either directly or subliminally, in society.\\\"\", \"from\": 9442, \"to\": 9508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that message\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9461}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 9499, \"to\": 9506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis would confide his status to only a select number of individuals for seven years.\", \"from\": 9509, \"to\": 9598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 9509, \"to\": 9517}, {\"ngram\": \"his status\", \"from\": 9532, \"to\": 9542}, {\"ngram\": \"only a select number\", \"from\": 9546, \"to\": 9566}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 9570, \"to\": 9581}, {\"ngram\": \"seven years\", \"from\": 9586, \"to\": 9597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming out to the world atthe peak of the AIDS crisismarked a turning point in Louganis' life.\", \"from\": 9600, \"to\": 9694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 9614, \"to\": 9623}, {\"ngram\": \"atthe peak\", \"from\": 9624, \"to\": 9634}, {\"ngram\": \"the AIDS\", \"from\": 9638, \"to\": 9646}, {\"ngram\": \"a turning point\", \"from\": 9660, \"to\": 9675}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' life\", \"from\": 9679, \"to\": 9693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had been famous since he was a teenager and a sex symbol for just as long, a tousled Californian with a movie star smile.\", \"from\": 9695, \"to\": 9819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 9727, \"to\": 9737}, {\"ngram\": \"a sex symbol\", \"from\": 9742, \"to\": 9754}, {\"ngram\": \"a tousled Californian\", \"from\": 9773, \"to\": 9794}, {\"ngram\": \"a movie star smile\", \"from\": 9800, \"to\": 9818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd never been closeted, exactly, but he'd been quiet about his sexuality in his early career.\", \"from\": 9820, \"to\": 9915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sexuality\", \"from\": 9881, \"to\": 9894}, {\"ngram\": \"his early career\", \"from\": 9898, \"to\": 9914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there was a subtle expectation on him to keep it that way.\", \"from\": 9916, \"to\": 9978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a subtle expectation\", \"from\": 9930, \"to\": 9950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I signed on with William Morris Agency,\\\" he says, \\\"They did say, 'Tone the gay thing down.\\\"\", \"from\": 9979, \"to\": 10076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10002, \"end\": 10023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Morris_Agency\", \"score\": 0.9999999999624833, \"rank\": 3.747141610356702e-11, \"text\": \"William Morris Agency\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Morris_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Morris_Agency\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gay thing\", \"from\": 10056, \"to\": 10069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was out to most friends and family,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 10078, \"to\": 10126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most friends\", \"from\": 10092, \"to\": 10104}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 10109, \"to\": 10115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My thinking back then was, well, everybody's entitled to a private life.\", \"from\": 10127, \"to\": 10200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My thinking\", \"from\": 10128, \"to\": 10139}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 10161, \"to\": 10170}, {\"ngram\": \"a private life\", \"from\": 10185, \"to\": 10199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that was my private life.\\\"\", \"from\": 10201, \"to\": 10230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my private life\", \"from\": 10213, \"to\": 10228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that private life had an additional, darker dimension - Louganis had spent several years in an abusive relationship with the man who was also his manager, a man who had once raped him at knifepoint.\", \"from\": 10232, \"to\": 10434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that private life\", \"from\": 10236, \"to\": 10253}, {\"ngram\": \"an additional, darker dimension\", \"from\": 10258, \"to\": 10289}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 10292, \"to\": 10300}, {\"ngram\": \"several years\", \"from\": 10311, \"to\": 10324}, {\"ngram\": \"an abusive relationship\", \"from\": 10328, \"to\": 10351}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 10357, \"to\": 10364}, {\"ngram\": \"his manager\", \"from\": 10378, \"to\": 10389}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 10391, \"to\": 10396}, {\"ngram\": \"knifepoint\", \"from\": 10423, \"to\": 10433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My view of the world was through the lenses of Jim,\\\" he explains.\", \"from\": 10435, \"to\": 10501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My view\", \"from\": 10436, \"to\": 10443}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 10447, \"to\": 10456}, {\"ngram\": \"the lenses\", \"from\": 10469, \"to\": 10479}, {\"ngram\": \"Jim\", \"from\": 10483, \"to\": 10486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't allowed to go out, unless I had permission.\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 10544, \"to\": 10554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jim [the late James \\\"Jim\\\" Babbitt] would go, but I wasn't allowed.\", \"from\": 10556, \"to\": 10622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10570, \"end\": 10575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.4184011961564578, \"rank\": 0.7033135604890223, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_II_of_England\"}, {\"begin\": 10582, \"end\": 10589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milton_Babbitt\", \"score\": 0.9995401365874045, \"rank\": 0.0002598788535439873, \"text\": \"Babbitt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milton_Babbitt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milton_Babbitt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jim\", \"from\": 10556, \"to\": 10559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is part of an abusive relationship, and also rape,\\\" he notes.\", \"from\": 10623, \"to\": 10689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 10631, \"to\": 10635}, {\"ngram\": \"an abusive relationship\", \"from\": 10639, \"to\": 10662}, {\"ngram\": \"also rape\", \"from\": 10668, \"to\": 10677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not about the sexual act, it's about control.\", \"from\": 10690, \"to\": 10741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sexual act\", \"from\": 10706, \"to\": 10720}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 10733, \"to\": 10740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about ultimate control.\\\"\", \"from\": 10742, \"to\": 10771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ultimate control\", \"from\": 10753, \"to\": 10769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Louganis petting his 2 Great Dane dogs while lying in grass in 1996.\", \"from\": 10773, \"to\": 10846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10773, \"end\": 10786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his 2 Great Dane dogs\", \"from\": 10795, \"to\": 10816}, {\"ngram\": \"grass\", \"from\": 10832, \"to\": 10837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(John Storey/Getty Images) Louganis' decision to go public about his identity and his diagnosis were undeniable acts of bravery.\", \"from\": 10847, \"to\": 10976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10848, \"end\": 10859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Storey_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.9925980228853288, \"rank\": 0.007440476190475775, \"text\": \"John Storey\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Storey_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Storey_(politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 10860, \"end\": 10865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.6901881538166642, \"rank\": 0.36726543006433765, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his identity\", \"from\": 10912, \"to\": 10924}, {\"ngram\": \"his diagnosis\", \"from\": 10929, \"to\": 10942}, {\"ngram\": \"undeniable acts\", \"from\": 10948, \"to\": 10963}, {\"ngram\": \"bravery\", \"from\": 10967, \"to\": 10974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were entwined with one of emancipation.\", \"from\": 10977, \"to\": 11021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"emancipation\", \"from\": 11008, \"to\": 11020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was diagnosed HIV-positive, it was like, who else will ever touch me?\", \"from\": 11022, \"to\": 11099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought, OK, I am stuck.\", \"from\": 11100, \"to\": 11126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is it, I will make do.\\\"\", \"from\": 11127, \"to\": 11155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, though, fed up Babbitt's mistreatment and the discovery that he'd also beensiphoning off most of his earnings, Louganis ended things.\", \"from\": 11156, \"to\": 11301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11183, \"end\": 11190