: 11574, \"to\": 11580}, {\"ngram\": \"uncaring slut\", \"from\": 11611, \"to\": 11624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis had toseek a restraining order, claiming he \\\"feared for his life\\\".\", \"from\": 11633, \"to\": 11708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 11633, \"to\": 11641}, {\"ngram\": \"a restraining order\", \"from\": 11653, \"to\": 11672}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 11698, \"to\": 11706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They eventually reached a settlement.\", \"from\": 11709, \"to\": 11746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a settlement\", \"from\": 11733, \"to\": 11745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Babbitt died of AIDS complications in 1990.\", \"from\": 11747, \"to\": 11790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11747, \"end\": 11754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\", \"score\": 0.7746725534722515, \"rank\": 0.2798931330918042, \"text\": \"Babbitt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AIDS complications\", \"from\": 11763, \"to\": 11781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His HIV disclosure, on Louganis' own terms and in his own time, was met at the time with an outpouring of support and praise around the world, along with some serious backlash.\", \"from\": 11792, \"to\": 11968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His HIV disclosure\", \"from\": 11792, \"to\": 11810}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' own terms\", \"from\": 11815, \"to\": 11834}, {\"ngram\": \"his own time\", \"from\": 11842, \"to\": 11854}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 11867, \"to\": 11875}, {\"ngram\": \"an outpouring\", \"from\": 11881, \"to\": 11894}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 11898, \"to\": 11905}, {\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 11910, \"to\": 11916}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 11924, \"to\": 11933}, {\"ngram\": \"some serious backlash\", \"from\": 11946, \"to\": 11967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that Louganis had cut himself when he hit his head in Seoul became a particular flashpoint.\", \"from\": 11969, \"to\": 12069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12032, \"end\": 12037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9933534985894863, \"rank\": 0.006690480953172582, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 11969, \"to\": 11977}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 11983, \"to\": 11991}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 12020, \"to\": 12028}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular flashpoint\", \"from\": 12045, \"to\": 12068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is really regrettable that he competed in the final round of the Olympics if he knew he was HIV-positive,\\\" Seoul Olympic Organizing Committee chairman Park Seh-jiktold Reuters in 1995.\", \"from\": 12070, \"to\": 12258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12181, \"end\": 12215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul_Olympic_Organizing_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seoul Olympic Organizing Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul_Olympic_Organizing_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul_Olympic_Organizing_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 12242, \"end\": 12249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999997753323239, \"rank\": 2.1664364922645086e-07, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final round\", \"from\": 12116, \"to\": 12131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 12135, \"to\": 12147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not morally right, particularly because he was injured and bled.\\\"\", \"from\": 12259, \"to\": 12331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis did not know the full extent of the controversy until years later.\", \"from\": 12333, \"to\": 12408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 12333, \"to\": 12341}, {\"ngram\": \"the full extent\", \"from\": 12355, \"to\": 12370}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 12374, \"to\": 12389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When my now ex-husband said, 'They tried to take your medals away,' I said, 'What?''\", \"from\": 12409, \"to\": 12494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ex\", \"from\": 12422, \"to\": 12424}, {\"ngram\": \"husband\", \"from\": 12425, \"to\": 12432}, {\"ngram\": \"your medals\", \"from\": 12459, \"to\": 12470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"he recalls.\", \"from\": 12495, \"to\": 12506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And he's like, 'Yeah, back then they tried to take your medals away, because they said you should not have been in Seoul, becausethey had a travel ban for HIV.'\\\"\", \"from\": 12507, \"to\": 12669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12623, \"end\": 12628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9933534985894863, \"rank\": 0.006690480953172582, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your medals\", \"from\": 12559, \"to\": 12570}, {\"ngram\": \"becausethey\", \"from\": 12630, \"to\": 12641}, {\"ngram\": \"a travel ban\", \"from\": 12646, \"to\": 12658}, {\"ngram\": \"HIV\", \"from\": 12663, \"to\": 12666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Though there was some public discourse about it at the time, the Olympic Committee itself did not move to strip Louganis of his medals.)\", \"from\": 12670, \"to\": 12807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some public discourse\", \"from\": 12688, \"to\": 12709}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 12722, \"to\": 12730}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 12732, \"to\": 12753}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 12783, \"to\": 12791}, {\"ngram\": \"his medals\", \"from\": 12795, \"to\": 12805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like a throwaway child.\", \"from\": 12809, \"to\": 12840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a throwaway child\", \"from\": 12822, \"to\": 12839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[\\u2026] I found out that she did not hold me after I was born.\\\"\", \"from\": 12841, \"to\": 12900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As he moved through his Olympic competition era and into the advocate and mentor phase of his life, Louganis reckoned with deeply rooted self-image issues.\", \"from\": 12902, \"to\": 13057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic competition era\", \"from\": 12922, \"to\": 12949}, {\"ngram\": \"the advocate and mentor phase\", \"from\": 12959, \"to\": 12988}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 12992, \"to\": 13000}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 13002, \"to\": 13010}, {\"ngram\": \"deeply rooted self-image issues\", \"from\": 13025, \"to\": 13056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up knowing that he'd been given up for adoption and spent his first nine months in foster care, Louganis says, \\\"I felt like a throwaway child.\\\"\", \"from\": 13058, \"to\": 13209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adoption\", \"from\": 13105, \"to\": 13113}, {\"ngram\": \"his first nine months\", \"from\": 13124, \"to\": 13145}, {\"ngram\": \"foster care\", \"from\": 13149, \"to\": 13160}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 13162, \"to\": 13170}, {\"ngram\": \"a throwaway child\", \"from\": 13190, \"to\": 13207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 24, he met his birth father, launching a relationship with him, his half-siblings and extended family that he says over time \\\"changed the trajectory of what's family to me.\\\"\", \"from\": 13210, \"to\": 13386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his birth father\", \"from\": 13224, \"to\": 13240}, {\"ngram\": \"a relationship\", \"from\": 13252, \"to\": 13266}, {\"ngram\": \"his half-siblings\", \"from\": 13277, \"to\": 13294}, {\"ngram\": \"extended family\", \"from\": 13299, \"to\": 13314}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 13333, \"to\": 13337}, {\"ngram\": \"the trajectory\", \"from\": 13347, \"to\": 13361}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 13372, \"to\": 13378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also worked on the anger he felt toward his birth mother.\", \"from\": 13388, \"to\": 13448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the anger\", \"from\": 13406, \"to\": 13415}, {\"ngram\": \"his birth mother\", \"from\": 13431, \"to\": 13447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I found out that she did not hold me after I was born,\\\" he says, sounding still wounded at the knowledge.\", \"from\": 13449, \"to\": 13555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knowledge\", \"from\": 13541, \"to\": 13554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But her parents told her that I was already adopted by a mixed-race couple because they knew I was going to be dark, because my father was Samoan.\", \"from\": 13556, \"to\": 13703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13696, \"end\": 13702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"score\": 0.9992409131196254, \"rank\": 0.0007579218860499839, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her parents\", \"from\": 13561, \"to\": 13572}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixed-race couple\", \"from\": 13612, \"to\": 13631}, {\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 13682, \"to\": 13691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were, from the sounds of it, quite racist.\", \"from\": 13704, \"to\": 13751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sounds\", \"from\": 13720, \"to\": 13730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not know.\\\"\", \"from\": 13752, \"to\": 13770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He says now he had \\\"a lot of forgiving to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 13771, \"to\": 13817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 13791, \"to\": 13796}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiving\", \"from\": 13800, \"to\": 13809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through meditation practice, it came to me that she could not give what she so desperately wanted for herself.\", \"from\": 13819, \"to\": 13930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"meditation practice\", \"from\": 13828, \"to\": 13847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then the tears started flowing, because she was scared.\", \"from\": 13931, \"to\": 13986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tears\", \"from\": 13936, \"to\": 13945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was only 16 when she had me.\", \"from\": 13987, \"to\": 14019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I could feel some compassion and empathy for her.\", \"from\": 14020, \"to\": 14074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some compassion\", \"from\": 14038, \"to\": 14053}, {\"ngram\": \"empathy\", \"from\": 14058, \"to\": 14065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's where a lot of forgiveness comes from.\", \"from\": 14075, \"to\": 14128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 14096, \"to\": 14101}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 14105, \"to\": 14116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meaningful forgiveness is to tap into the compassion and empathy,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 14129, \"to\": 14204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meaningful forgiveness\", \"from\": 14129, \"to\": 14151}, {\"ngram\": \"the compassion\", \"from\": 14167, \"to\": 14181}, {\"ngram\": \"empathy\", \"from\": 14186, \"to\": 14193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also found similar compassion for his former partner.\", \"from\": 14206, \"to\": 14262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similar compassion\", \"from\": 14220, \"to\": 14238}, {\"ngram\": \"his former partner\", \"from\": 14243, \"to\": 14261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could come to a place of forgiveness,\\\" he says, \\\"because hurt people hurt people.\", \"from\": 14263, \"to\": 14347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 14280, \"to\": 14287}, {\"ngram\": \"forgiveness\", \"from\": 14291, \"to\": 14302}, {\"ngram\": \"hurt people\", \"from\": 14323, \"to\": 14334}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 14340, \"to\": 14346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, there was a tremendous amount of hurt there.\", \"from\": 14348, \"to\": 14403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tremendous amount\", \"from\": 14369, \"to\": 14388}, {\"ngram\": \"hurt\", \"from\": 14392, \"to\": 14396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Jim, I wasn't always sure what he said was true.\", \"from\": 14404, \"to\": 14457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jim\", \"from\": 14409, \"to\": 14412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I think one of the truths that he shared is that he was as a child molested by his stepfather.\", \"from\": 14458, \"to\": 14556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truths\", \"from\": 14477, \"to\": 14487}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 14521, \"to\": 14528}, {\"ngram\": \"his stepfather\", \"from\": 14541, \"to\": 14555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just imagine a young boy who did not feel he had power, and then somebody dominating him like that.\", \"from\": 14557, \"to\": 14656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young boy\", \"from\": 14570, \"to\": 14581}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 14606, \"to\": 14611}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 14622, \"to\": 14630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That must have been really, really difficult.\", \"from\": 14657, \"to\": 14702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are supposed to be able to trust your parents.\", \"from\": 14703, \"to\": 14753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your parents\", \"from\": 14740, \"to\": 14752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That trust was broken, so you can understand where it came from.\\\"\", \"from\": 14754, \"to\": 14819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That trust\", \"from\": 14754, \"to\": 14764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows it does not excuse what Babbitt did to him; it just enables him to move forward from it.\", \"from\": 14821, \"to\": 14918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14854, \"end\": 14861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\", \"score\": 0.7208516039314561, \"rank\": 0.27339820771470424, \"text\": \"Babbitt\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irving_Babbitt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have also come to learn and accept and realize we can not change other people,\\\" he says, \\\"no matter how hard we try.\\\"\", \"from\": 14919, \"to\": 15039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 14987, \"to\": 14999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Louganis first learned he had HIV, he says, \\\"I [sold] my life insurance policyso I could travel and do whatever, because I did not expect to be here.\", \"from\": 15041, \"to\": 15195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 15046, \"to\": 15054}, {\"ngram\": \"HIV\", \"from\": 15076, \"to\": 15079}, {\"ngram\": \"my life insurance policyso\", \"from\": 15100, \"to\": 15126}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 15149, \"to\": 15157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All these years later, it's like, s**t, I have got to get a job.\", \"from\": 15196, \"to\": 15260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 15254, \"to\": 15259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now what do I do?\\\"\", \"from\": 15261, \"to\": 15279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis' energy now is often now devoted to his coaching and speaking engagements, as well as his other careertraining canines.\", \"from\": 15281, \"to\": 15409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis' energy\", \"from\": 15281, \"to\": 15297}, {\"ngram\": \"his coaching and speaking engagements\", \"from\": 15326, \"to\": 15363}, {\"ngram\": \"his other careertraining canines\", \"from\": 15376, \"to\": 15408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(In 1999, he published a pet owner's guidebook called\\\"For the Life of Your Dog.\\\")\", \"from\": 15410, \"to\": 15491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pet owner's guidebook\", \"from\": 15433, \"to\": 15456}, {\"ngram\": \"called\\\"For\", \"from\": 15457, \"to\": 15467}, {\"ngram\": \"the Life\", \"from\": 15468, \"to\": 15476}, {\"ngram\": \"Your Dog\", \"from\": 15480, \"to\": 15488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, his put three of his Olympic medals up for auction, hoping to donate a portion of the proceeds tothe HIV/AIDS organization Damien Center.\", \"from\": 15492, \"to\": 15640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic medals\", \"from\": 15520, \"to\": 15538}, {\"ngram\": \"auction\", \"from\": 15546, \"to\": 15553}, {\"ngram\": \"a portion\", \"from\": 15572, \"to\": 15581}, {\"ngram\": \"the proceeds\", \"from\": 15585, \"to\": 15597}, {\"ngram\": \"tothe HIV/AIDS organization Damien Center\", \"from\": 15598, \"to\": 15639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was obviously a financial thing,\\\" he says candidly, \\\"and hoping to raise money to help the Damien Center so that they could do some good.\", \"from\": 15641, \"to\": 15782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a financial thing\", \"from\": 15659, \"to\": 15676}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 15718, \"to\": 15723}, {\"ngram\": \"the Damien Center\", \"from\": 15732, \"to\": 15749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But also help me out as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 15783, \"to\": 15813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Greg Louganis speaks onstage during the Los Angeles LGBT Center 47th Anniversary Gala Vanguard Awards at Pacific Design Center on September 24, 2016 in West Hollywood.\", \"from\": 15815, \"to\": 15982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15815, \"end\": 15828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}, {\"begin\": 15855, \"end\": 15878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles LGBT Center\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 15920, \"end\": 15941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Design_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pacific Design Center\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Design_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Design_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 15967, \"end\": 15981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood\", \"score\": 0.999691111190731, \"rank\": 0.0003089750371474584, \"text\": \"West Hollywood\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 15945, \"to\": 15954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Joe Scarnici/Getty Images for Los Angeles LGBT Center) He continues, soberly, \\\"I have fought so many battles.\", \"from\": 15983, \"to\": 16094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15984, \"end\": 15987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Duplantier\", \"score\": 0.9546114154684171, \"rank\": 0.027866307877282812, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Duplantier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Duplantier\"}, {\"begin\": 16014, \"end\": 16037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles LGBT Center\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_LGBT_Center\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many battles\", \"from\": 16077, \"to\": 16092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just tired.\", \"from\": 16095, \"to\": 16111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tired of fighting.\", \"from\": 16112, \"to\": 16130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have not I accomplished enough?\", \"from\": 16131, \"to\": 16162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have not I made a big enough difference?\", \"from\": 16163, \"to\": 16203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big enough difference\", \"from\": 16179, \"to\": 16202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can not I just be done?\", \"from\": 16204, \"to\": 16227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It really is kind of a weird space that I am in.\", \"from\": 16228, \"to\": 16276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of a weird space\", \"from\": 16241, \"to\": 16262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People say, because I am 64, 'midlife awakening or midlife crisis?'\", \"from\": 16277, \"to\": 16344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 16277, \"to\": 16283}, {\"ngram\": \"64, 'midlife awakening\", \"from\": 16302, \"to\": 16324}, {\"ngram\": \"midlife crisis\", \"from\": 16328, \"to\": 16342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It certainly feels crisis-y more often than I'd like it to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 16345, \"to\": 16408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crisis-y\", \"from\": 16364, \"to\": 16372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soon, however, he rouses himself.\", \"from\": 16410, \"to\": 16443, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's where I am at now,\\\" he admits.\", \"from\": 16444, \"to\": 16482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am questioning, and trying to figure some things out.\", \"from\": 16483, \"to\": 16539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some things\", \"from\": 16523, \"to\": 16534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like I said, is this an awakening or crisis?\", \"from\": 16540, \"to\": 16584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an awakening\", \"from\": 16561, \"to\": 16573}, {\"ngram\": \"crisis\", \"from\": 16577, \"to\": 16583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels like a crisis so often, and it's like, 'Well, what do I do?\", \"from\": 16585, \"to\": 16653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crisis\", \"from\": 16599, \"to\": 16607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How can I help others?'\", \"from\": 16654, \"to\": 16677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 16669, \"to\": 16675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We went to elementary schools that last couple of weeks for Olympic Day, and it was so great to connect with the kids.\", \"from\": 16678, \"to\": 16796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elementary schools\", \"from\": 16689, \"to\": 16707}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 16728, \"to\": 16733}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Day\", \"from\": 16738, \"to\": 16749}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 16787, \"to\": 16795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's important to have that outreach, and make those outreach points much more available.\\\"\", \"from\": 16797, \"to\": 16887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that outreach\", \"from\": 16820, \"to\": 16833}, {\"ngram\": \"those outreach\", \"from\": 16844, \"to\": 16858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about what he believes will be his legacy, Louganis is reflective.\", \"from\": 16889, \"to\": 16966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his legacy\", \"from\": 16931, \"to\": 16941}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 16943, \"to\": 16951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think my perceived legacy is obviously diving.\", \"from\": 16967, \"to\": 17016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my perceived legacy\", \"from\": 16976, \"to\": 16995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if they remember me as a diver, I hope that I am remembered as being strong and graceful,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 17017, \"to\": 17120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a diver\", \"from\": 17044, \"to\": 17051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But my legacy as a person, I would hope people would say I was kind.\", \"from\": 17121, \"to\": 17190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 17139, \"to\": 17147}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 17162, \"to\": 17168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making a difference, that's a lot, and it's also very subjective.\", \"from\": 17191, \"to\": 17256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 17198, \"to\": 17210}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 17219, \"to\": 17224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But kind?\", \"from\": 17257, \"to\": 17266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can always be kind.\\\"\", \"from\": 17267, \"to\": 17291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to see my records broken.\", \"from\": 17293, \"to\": 17326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my records\", \"from\": 17308, \"to\": 17318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's awesome.\\\"\", \"from\": 17327, \"to\": 17351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That imperative to kindness comes through in the way Louganis speaks, with a gentle southern California cadence and regular pauses to carefully collect his words.\", \"from\": 17353, \"to\": 17515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17446, \"end\": 17456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999954762436123, \"rank\": 2.0524193979911323e-06, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 17372, \"to\": 17380}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 17398, \"to\": 17405}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 17406, \"to\": 17414}, {\"ngram\": \"regular pauses\", \"from\": 17469, \"to\": 17483}, {\"ngram\": \"his words\", \"from\": 17505, \"to\": 17514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's there in the way he cites his dogs as inspiration.\", \"from\": 17516, \"to\": 17571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 17530, \"to\": 17537}, {\"ngram\": \"his dogs\", \"from\": 17547, \"to\": 17555}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 17559, \"to\": 17570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are great teachers,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 17572, \"to\": 17607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great teachers\", \"from\": 17582, \"to\": 17596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They do not hold on to resentments.\", \"from\": 17608, \"to\": 17644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"resentments\", \"from\": 17632, \"to\": 17643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not judge.\", \"from\": 17645, \"to\": 17663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are just grateful for whatever they have.\\\"\", \"from\": 17664, \"to\": 17711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 17691, \"to\": 17699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis is also conscious of his role as an elder statesman, for both the LGBTQ+ community and athletics.\", \"from\": 17713, \"to\": 17819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 17713, \"to\": 17721}, {\"ngram\": \"his role\", \"from\": 17743, \"to\": 17751}, {\"ngram\": \"an elder statesman\", \"from\": 17755, \"to\": 17773}, {\"ngram\": \"both the LGBTQ+ community\", \"from\": 17779, \"to\": 17804}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 17809, \"to\": 17818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He acknowledges that he's concerned about the threats to LGBTQ+ rights in America, but says, \\\"You can not close up the Pandora's Box, once it's opened.\", \"from\": 17820, \"to\": 17971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the threats\", \"from\": 17862, \"to\": 17873}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ rights\", \"from\": 17877, \"to\": 17890}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 17894, \"to\": 17901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pandora's Box\", \"from\": 17935, \"to\": 17952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not going to go backward.\", \"from\": 17972, \"to\": 18004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's ridiculous.\\\"\", \"from\": 18005, \"to\": 18024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He adds, however, \\\"The divisiveness that it stirs up, and the anger or rage that comes with that, I do not understand it.\", \"from\": 18025, \"to\": 18146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why would it threaten you?\", \"from\": 18147, \"to\": 18173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not really, truly affecting you.\", \"from\": 18174, \"to\": 18211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The thing that concerns me most is the visceral hate and anger, because that's so, so devastating.\", \"from\": 18212, \"to\": 18310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The thing\", \"from\": 18212, \"to\": 18221}, {\"ngram\": \"the visceral hate\", \"from\": 18247, \"to\": 18264}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 18269, \"to\": 18274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's hard for me to understand.\\\"\", \"from\": 18311, \"to\": 18343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And when he contemplates this year's Olympics, Louganis offers a unique viewpoint, including his opinions on thecurrent controversies over the use of performance-enhancing resources.\", \"from\": 18345, \"to\": 18527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympics\", \"from\": 18370, \"to\": 18390}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 18392, \"to\": 18400}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique viewpoint\", \"from\": 18408, \"to\": 18426}, {\"ngram\": \"his opinions\", \"from\": 18438, \"to\": 18450}, {\"ngram\": \"thecurrent controversies\", \"from\": 18454, \"to\": 18478}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 18484, \"to\": 18491}, {\"ngram\": \"performance-enhancing resources\", \"from\": 18495, \"to\": 18526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was 33, we did not know what was going on with me,\\\" he remembers.\", \"from\": 18528, \"to\": 18601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was wasting.\", \"from\": 18602, \"to\": 18617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growth hormone was helpful to get my energy back up.\", \"from\": 18618, \"to\": 18670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Growth hormone\", \"from\": 18618, \"to\": 18632}, {\"ngram\": \"my energy\", \"from\": 18652, \"to\": 18661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of the medications that helped me push through some of my treatments, they were actually lifesaving.\\\"\", \"from\": 18671, \"to\": 18778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medications\", \"from\": 18680, \"to\": 18695}, {\"ngram\": \"my treatments\", \"from\": 18732, \"to\": 18745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Diver, a sculpture by U.S. artist Carole Feuerman on display in Paris on July 22, 2024, ahead of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 18780, \"to\": 18910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18818, \"end\": 18833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carole_Feuerman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carole Feuerman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carole_Feuerman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carole_Feuerman\"}, {\"begin\": 18848, \"end\": 18853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999941729813, \"rank\": 5.826824470718413e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Diver\", \"from\": 18780, \"to\": 18789}, {\"ngram\": \"a sculpture\", \"from\": 18791, \"to\": 18802}, {\"ngram\": \"display\", \"from\": 18837, \"to\": 18844}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 18857, \"to\": 18861}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 18881, \"to\": 18909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Feuerman was inspired by U.S. diver Greg Louganis, a four-time Olympic medalist at the 1984 and 1988 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 18911, \"to\": 19026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18947, \"end\": 18960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Louganis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Louganis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Feuerman\", \"from\": 18911, \"to\": 18919}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-time Olympic medalist\", \"from\": 18962, \"to\": 18990}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1984 and 1988 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 18994, \"to\": 19025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Christophe DELATTRE / AFP)Louganis notes, \\\"When somebody says, 'What if your records are broken, and you find out that they are juicing, or taking something?'\", \"from\": 19027, \"to\": 19186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christophe\", \"from\": 19028, \"to\": 19038}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP)Louganis\", \"from\": 19050, \"to\": 19062}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 19076, \"to\": 19084}, {\"ngram\": \"your records\", \"from\": 19100, \"to\": 19112}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 19175, \"to\": 19184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to find out what they are taking!\", \"from\": 19187, \"to\": 19227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's great.\", \"from\": 19228, \"to\": 19241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to see my records broken.\", \"from\": 19242, \"to\": 19274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my records\", \"from\": 19256, \"to\": 19266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether they do that aided by something, it would not matter to me, personally, because I think that's awesome.\", \"from\": 19275, \"to\": 19386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 19305, \"to\": 19314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because then we find great information.\\\"\", \"from\": 19387, \"to\": 19427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great information\", \"from\": 19408, \"to\": 19425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many in the field dissent with Louganis' view, particularly supporters of the World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA), an independent agency created to \\\"fight against doping in sport,\\\" a problem it describes as\\\"a scourge.\", \"from\": 19429, \"to\": 19642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19507, \"end\": 19538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 19507, \"end\": 19538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field dissent\", \"from\": 19437, \"to\": 19454}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis' view\", \"from\": 19460, \"to\": 19474}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly supporters\", \"from\": 19476, \"to\": 19499}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent agency\", \"from\": 19540, \"to\": 19561}, {\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 19588, \"to\": 19594}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 19598, \"to\": 19603}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 19606, \"to\": 19615}, {\"ngram\": \"as\\\"a scourge\", \"from\": 19629, \"to\": 19641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But WADA has come under fire this summer, with pushback againstits ruling over Chinese athletesrevealing how far from black and white the metrics of testing, and ideas of what constitutes doping, can be.\", \"from\": 19642, \"to\": 19846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WADA\", \"from\": 19647, \"to\": 19651}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 19667, \"to\": 19671}, {\"ngram\": \"pushback againstits\", \"from\": 19690, \"to\": 19709}, {\"ngram\": \"the metrics\", \"from\": 19777, \"to\": 19788}, {\"ngram\": \"testing\", \"from\": 19792, \"to\": 19799}, {\"ngram\": \"ideas\", \"from\": 19805, \"to\": 19810}, {\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 19831, \"to\": 19837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Louganis says, \\\"I am not fully on board withthe whole WADA thing.\", \"from\": 19848, \"to\": 19913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 19848, \"to\": 19856}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 19882, \"to\": 19887}, {\"ngram\": \"whole WADA thing\", \"from\": 19896, \"to\": 19912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have demonized it as cheating.\", \"from\": 19914, \"to\": 19947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, what if it wasn't cheating?\", \"from\": 19948, \"to\": 19981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The drugs are not showing up to the training sessions; the athlete is putting the work in.\", \"from\": 19982, \"to\": 20072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The drugs\", \"from\": 19982, \"to\": 19991}, {\"ngram\": \"the training sessions\", \"from\": 20014, \"to\": 20035}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 20037, \"to\": 20048}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 20060, \"to\": 20068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it's not a popular stance, but it's just my own personal awareness.\", \"from\": 20073, \"to\": 20147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a popular stance\", \"from\": 20089, \"to\": 20105}, {\"ngram\": \"my own personal awareness\", \"from\": 20121, \"to\": 20146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key is, if we are talking about it, if we have open communication about it, then it can be safe.\", \"from\": 20148, \"to\": 20248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key\", \"from\": 20148, \"to\": 20155}, {\"ngram\": \"open communication\", \"from\": 20199, \"to\": 20217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as we demonize it, and it's in the shadows, then that's where a lot of things can go awry, because they are trying to hide it.\", \"from\": 20249, \"to\": 20383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shadows\", \"from\": 20288, \"to\": 20299}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 20319, \"to\": 20324}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 20328, \"to\": 20334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If we are truly open about it, and really helping each other, then it could be terrific information that we gather to help the quality of life of others.\\\"\", \"from\": 20384, \"to\": 20538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terrific information\", \"from\": 20463, \"to\": 20483}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 20507, \"to\": 20518}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 20522, \"to\": 20526}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 20530, \"to\": 20536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while the current crop of very young competitors in Paris has raised questions about age limits andconcern over pushing kids too hard too soon, Louganis likewise offers another perspective.\", \"from\": 20540, \"to\": 20733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20596, \"end\": 20601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999443998697771, \"rank\": 5.5603221641646716e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current crop\", \"from\": 20550, \"to\": 20566}, {\"ngram\": \"very young competitors\", \"from\": 20570, \"to\": 20592}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 20613, \"to\": 20622}, {\"ngram\": \"age limits\", \"from\": 20629, \"to\": 20639}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 20664, \"to\": 20668}, {\"ngram\": \"Louganis\", \"from\": 20688, \"to\": 20696}, {\"ngram\": \"another perspective\", \"from\": 20713, \"to\": 20732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For him, finding the diving board at an early age was salvation.\", \"from\": 20734, \"to\": 20798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the diving board\", \"from\": 20751, \"to\": 20767}, {\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 20771, \"to\": 20783}, {\"ngram\": \"salvation\", \"from\": 20788, \"to\": 20797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot of people try to convince me that I sacrificed my childhood.\", \"from\": 20800, \"to\": 20875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 20809, \"to\": 20814}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 20818, \"to\": 20824}, {\"ngram\": \"my childhood\", \"from\": 20862, \"to\": 20874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one thing that my mother was always very clear with me is that we are a product of the decisions that we make, no matter how you come to make those choices.\", \"from\": 20876, \"to\": 21036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 20880, \"to\": 20889}, {\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 20895, \"to\": 20904}, {\"ngram\": \"a product\", \"from\": 20950, \"to\": 20959